{
  "stem": "4764.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the other thing I remember was that I couldn't understand, when my father said there was a world outside-- like we had an Aunt in America-- I said, well, why can't she come and help us?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, why don't the other people come and help you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was an article about the fact that they didn't bomb Auschwitz, the Allies never bombed Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Otherwise they would have got rid of the-- they would have killed a lot of people, but they would have got rid of the ovens, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I suppose it was politics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm not sure whether there were-- there was any way to escape any-- I think it was a more resignation of-- of going back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then there was news started filtering about the Russians and the war coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- there was-- this was '43, '44, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was already-- there was some-- I mean, there was information coming through that, obviously, the war is-- was going to come to an end fairly soon, right?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a question of survival until that happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that the Russians were coming from the east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, actually, we were rescued by-- liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people from-- these-- people in this-- this officious looking office building just left one day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next thing I remember was I was taken out of this barn where I was sitting and listening to the reports of the fruit prices.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a lot of sort of soldiers running around this little village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wore this very strange uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't look like the Germans, because the Germans were very well-dressed and kept with high boots.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
